CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 15, 1970, pg. 23, reads: "NAACP Youth Council Parade - When the Pittsburgh Branch NAACP Youth Council sponsored its annual Black Arts Festival recently, the event was led off by a parade through the Hill District of Pittsburgh. The New Pittsburgh Courier participated with a booth and also in parade...  Holding aloft the banner of the New Pittsburgh Courier in the second photo, are Keith Morris, (left) and Charles Ray... - All Harris photos.
TitMainTitle: Keith Morris and Charles Ray holding New Pittsburgh Courier banner off end of car, in NAACP Youth Council parade
